With over 190 stores nationwide, Ernest Jones is firmly established as the UK’s diamond and watch specialist. You’ll find a breathtaking collection of exquisite diamonds, jewellery and designer gifts. We keep an eye on the latest trends and our fashion jewellery includes stunning cocktail rings and vintage-style pieces that your customers love to own. Ernest Jones stocks some of the world’s most prestigious watch brands, such as Omega, TAG Heuer, Breitling, Gucci, Chanel, Bell & Ross, Cartier and Longines. We have a team of watchmakers who have trained with some of the world’s most prestigious watch houses and offer the highest standard of service.  As well as diamonds, jewellery and watches, Ernest Jones has gifts for every occasion and luxury accessories from top brands including Mont Blanc, Alfred Dunhill and Hugo Boss.

